<p>**
Redux</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>state management system for cross-component or app-wide state
Redux vs React Context</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>React Context ë‹¨ì 
-Complex Setup/Management
-high-frequency changes makes low Performance</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>Redux
-Central Data(State) store
-Subscription
-Reducer Function mutates store data
-Components Dispatch Action, Actions are Forwarded to Reducer fuction -í•­ìƒ override state ë°©ì‹ìœ¼ë¡œ mutateí•´ì•¼ë§Œí•œë‹¤ ì£¼ì˜ !!(state immutability)
npm i redux react-redux
npm i @reduxjs/toolkit</p>
</blockquote>

